journalEntries.conceptsCovered: How to operate in the terminal, VScode, HTML
journalEntries.journalEntry: Today we learned how to make commands on the command line in the terminal including how to make directories and files and how to move from directory to directory. We also went over basic HTML as familarized ourselves with VSCODE our code editor
We went over methods for arrays such as sort, map, filter, reduce etc.
We covered deleting data in json through fetching.
Gathered with over students to study and catch up on work
